# English Only in Code

- All code comments must be written in English.
- All variable names, function names, and identifiers must be in English.
- All documentation files (README, CHANGELOG, etc.) must be written in English.
- All git commit messages must be written in English.
- User-facing strings (UI labels, error messages, placeholders) must also be written in English.
